<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Trace Pipeline — {{ scenario_name }}</title>
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/mermaid@10/dist/mermaid.min.js"></script>
<style>
:root{
  --ok:#10b981;--ok-bg:#ecfdf5;--ok-border:#a7f3d0;
  --fail:#ef4444;--fail-bg:#fef2f2;--fail-border:#fca5a5;
  --warn:#f59e0b;--warn-bg:#fffbeb;
  --blue:#3b82f6;--blue-bg:#eff6ff;
  --purple:#8b5cf6;--purple-bg:#f5f3ff;
  --gray:#6b7280;--gray-bg:#f9fafb;--gray-border:#e5e7eb;
  --text:#111827;--muted:#6b7280;
  --bg:#f3f4f6;--card:#fff;
  --r:8px;--sh:0 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,.1);
}
*{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
body{font-family:system-ui,-apple-system,sans-serif;background:var(--bg);color:var(--text);line-height:1.5}
code{font-family:'Cascadia Code','Fira Code',monospace;font-size:.82em;background:#f1f5f9;padding:1px 5px;border-radius:3px;word-break:break-all}
a{color:var(--blue);text-decoration:none}a:hover{text-decoration:underline}

/* header */
.hdr{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0f172a 0%,#1e1b4b 100%);color:#fff;padding:26px 36px}
.hdr-inner{max-width:1180px;margin:0 auto;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:flex-start;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:12px}
.hdr h1{font-size:1.4rem;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:4px}
.hdr-sub{font-size:.78rem;opacity:.6;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.08em;margin-bottom:5px}
.hdr-meta{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:16px;font-size:.82rem;opacity:.78;margin-top:8px}
.hdr-back{background:rgba(255,255,255,.12);color:#fff;padding:7px 16px;border-radius:6px;font-size:.85rem;font-weight:500;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.2)}
.hdr-back:hover{background:rgba(255,255,255,.2);text-decoration:none}
.status-pill{padding:5px 18px;border-radius:999px;font-weight:700;font-size:.95rem}
.status-pill.pass{background:#10b981;color:#fff}
.status-pill.fail{background:#ef4444;color:#fff}

.wrap{max-width:1180px;margin:0 auto;padding:28px 20px}

/* section titles */
.sec-title{font-size:1.05rem;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:14px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px}
.sec-title::before{content:'';display:block;width:4px;height:1.1em;background:var(--purple);border-radius:2px}

/* Architecture card */
.arch-card{background:var(--card);border-radius:var(--r);padding:22px 24px;margin-bottom:28px;box-shadow:var(--sh)}
.arch-subtitle{font-size:.82rem;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:16px}
.mermaid-wrap{overflow-x:auto}

/* Legend */
.legend{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:10px;margin-top:14px}
.leg-item{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;font-size:.78rem;color:var(--muted)}
.leg-dot{width:10px;height:10px;border-radius:50%}

/* Trace table */
.trace-card{background:var(--card);border-radius:var(--r);padding:22px 24px;box-shadow:var(--sh);overflow-x:auto}
table{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;font-size:.84rem}
th{background:#f8fafc;padding:9px 12px;text-align:left;font-size:.76rem;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.05em;color:var(--muted);border-bottom:2px solid var(--gray-border);white-space:nowrap}
td{padding:10px 12px;border-bottom:1px solid #f3f4f6;vertical-align:top}
tr:last-child td{border-bottom:none}
tr.ok-row{}
tr.fail-row{background:#fffbfb}

/* keyword pills */
.kw{padding:2px 8px;border-radius:4px;font-size:.72rem;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;white-space:nowrap}
.kw-given{background:#dbeafe;color:#1d4ed8}
.kw-when{background:#fef3c7;color:#92400e}
.kw-then{background:#d1fae5;color:#065f46}
.kw-and,.kw-but{background:#f3f4f6;color:#374151}

/* intent pill */
.intent{background:var(--purple-bg);color:#7c3aed;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:4px;font-size:.74rem;font-weight:600;white-space:nowrap}

/* entity tags */
.entity{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:3px;background:#f1f5f9;border:1px solid #e2e8f0;border-radius:4px;padding:1px 6px;font-size:.74rem;margin:2px}
.entity .ekey{color:var(--purple);font-weight:600}
.entity .eval{color:var(--text)}

/* code block */
.code-lines{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:3px}
.code-line{font-family:'Cascadia Code','Fira Code',monospace;font-size:.74rem;background:#f8fafc;border:1px solid #e2e8f0;border-radius:3px;padding:2px 6px;word-break:break-all}

/* method badge */
.method{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:4px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:999px;font-size:.74rem;font-weight:600;white-space:nowrap}
.m-direct{background:var(--gray-bg);color:var(--gray);border:1px solid var(--gray-border)}
.m-fallback{background:var(--purple-bg);color:#7c3aed;border:1px solid #ddd6fe}
.m-fallback-fail{background:var(--warn-bg);color:#92400e;border:1px solid #fde68a}
.m-retry{background:var(--blue-bg);color:#1d4ed8;border:1px solid #bfdbfe}
.m-fail{background:var(--fail-bg);color:var(--fail);border:1px solid var(--fail-border)}

/* status */
.st{padding:2px 10px;border-radius:999px;font-size:.74rem;font-weight:700}
.st-ok{background:var(--ok-bg);color:var(--ok);border:1px solid var(--ok-border)}
.st-fail{background:var(--fail-bg);color:var(--fail);border:1px solid var(--fail-border)}

/* error tooltip area */
.err-box{margin-top:5px;font-size:.76rem;color:var(--fail);max-width:320px}
.err-type{font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;font-size:.7rem;letter-spacing:.04em}
.err-exp{color:#7f1d1d;margin-top:2px}

/* duration bar */
.dur-bar{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;white-space:nowrap}
.bar{height:6px;border-radius:3px;background:var(--gray-border);overflow:hidden;width:60px}
.bar-fill{height:100%;border-radius:3px}
.ok-bar{background:var(--ok)}
.fail-bar{background:var(--fail)}

.footer{text-align:center;font-size:.78rem;color:var(--muted);margin-top:36px;padding-top:16px;border-top:1px solid var(--gray-border)}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- HEADER -->
<div class="hdr">
  <div class="hdr-inner">
    <div>
      <div class="hdr-sub">IA Test Agent · Trace d'exécution pipeline</div>
      <h1>{{ scenario_name }}</h1>
      <div class="hdr-meta">
        <span>📅 {{ date_generated }}</span>
        <span>⏱ {{ "%.0f"|format(duree_ms) }} ms</span>
        {% if url_cible %}<span>🌐 {{ url_cible }}</span>{% endif %}
        <span>🌍 {{ language }}</span>
        <span style="opacity:.5">id: {{ test_id }}</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;flex-shrink:0;padding-top:4px">
      {% if statut == 'PASSED' %}
      <span class="status-pill pass">✓ PASSED</span>
      {% else %}
      <span class="status-pill fail">✗ FAILED</span>
      {% endif %}
      <a class="hdr-back" href="report_{{ test_id }}.html">← Rapport</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="wrap">

  <!-- ── ARCHITECTURE DIAGRAM ── -->
  <div class="arch-card">
    <div class="sec-title">Architecture du pipeline IA</div>
    <div class="arch-subtitle">Flux de traitement de chaque scénario Gherkin</div>
    <div class="mermaid-wrap">
      <div class="mermaid">
flowchart LR
    U([👤 Utilisateur]):::usr --> GH["📋 Scénario Gherkin\nGiven / When / Then"]:::input
    GH --> NLP["🧠 NLP Service\nspaCy + Regex\n• Détection d'intention\n• Extraction d'entités"]:::nlp
    NLP --> GEN["⚙️ Generator Service\nPlaywright code\nget_by_role / locator / fill…"]:::gen
    GEN --> EXEC["▶ Executor Service\nExécution ligne par ligne"]:::exec

    EXEC --> D1{Playwright\ndirect}:::decision
    D1 -->|✓ OK| SOK(["✓ Step OK"]):::ok
    D1 -->|✗ Timeout| VIS["🔍 Vision Service\nYOLO + DOM F12\nScreenshot → Détection\néléments UI"]:::vis

    VIS --> D2{Élément\ntrouvé ?}:::decision
    D2 -->|Oui| ACT["🖱 Action via\ncoordonées\nou JS eval"]:::act
    ACT --> SOK2(["✓ Récupéré\n(visual_fallback)"]):::ok
    D2 -->|Non| ADP["🔄 Adaptation Service\nDiagnostic IA\n• popup_close\n• retry\n• screenshot_redetect"]:::adapt
    ADP --> D3{Retry\npossible ?}:::decision
    D3 -->|Oui| EXEC
    D3 -->|Non| SFAIL(["✗ Échec définitif"]):::fail

    classDef usr fill:#e0e7ff,stroke:#6366f1,color:#3730a3
    classDef input fill:#dbeafe,stroke:#3b82f6,color:#1e40af
    classDef nlp fill:#f5f3ff,stroke:#8b5cf6,color:#6d28d9
    classDef gen fill:#fef3c7,stroke:#f59e0b,color:#78350f
    classDef exec fill:#ecfdf5,stroke:#10b981,color:#065f46
    classDef vis fill:#fce7f3,stroke:#ec4899,color:#9d174d
    classDef act fill:#f0fdf4,stroke:#22c55e,color:#14532d
    classDef adapt fill:#fff7ed,stroke:#f97316,color:#7c2d12
    classDef decision fill:#f8fafc,stroke:#64748b,color:#334155
    classDef ok fill:#ecfdf5,stroke:#10b981,color:#065f46,font-weight:bold
    classDef fail fill:#fef2f2,stroke:#ef4444,color:#7f1d1d,font-weight:bold
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="legend">
      <div class="leg-item"><div class="leg-dot" style="background:#8b5cf6"></div> NLP (spaCy + Regex)</div>
      <div class="leg-item"><div class="leg-dot" style="background:#f59e0b"></div> Génération code Playwright</div>
      <div class="leg-item"><div class="leg-dot" style="background:#10b981"></div> Exécution directe (OK)</div>
      <div class="leg-item"><div class="leg-dot" style="background:#ec4899"></div> Fallback YOLO + DOM</div>
      <div class="leg-item"><div class="leg-dot" style="background:#f97316"></div> Adaptation + Retry</div>
      <div class="leg-item"><div class="leg-dot" style="background:#ef4444"></div> Échec définitif</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ── STEP TRACE TABLE ── -->
  <div class="trace-card">
    <div class="sec-title">Trace par step ({{ steps|length }} steps Gherkin)</div>

    <table>
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>#</th>
          <th>Step Gherkin</th>
          <th>NLP → Intention + Entités</th>
          <th>Code génération</th>
          <th>Méthode utilisée</th>
          <th>Statut</th>
          <th>Durée</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        {% for step in steps %}
        {% set is_ok = step.statut == 'OK' %}

        {# keyword class #}
        {% set kw_lower = step.keyword|lower %}
        {% if kw_lower == 'given' %}{% set kw_cls = 'kw-given' %}
        {% elif kw_lower == 'when' %}{% set kw_cls = 'kw-when' %}
        {% elif kw_lower == 'then' %}{% set kw_cls = 'kw-then' %}
        {% else %}{% set kw_cls = 'kw-and' %}{% endif %}

        {# method badge #}
        {% if step.method_used == 'visual_fallback' %}
          {% set m_cls = 'm-fallback' %}{% set m_lbl = '🔍 YOLO+DOM Fallback' %}
        {% elif step.method_used == 'visual_fallback_tried' %}
          {% set m_cls = 'm-fallback-fail' %}{% set m_lbl = '⚠ Fallback tenté (échec)' %}
        {% elif step.method_used == 'retry_adaptation' %}
          {% set m_cls = 'm-retry' %}{% set m_lbl = '🔄 Retry + Adaptation' %}
        {% elif step.method_used == 'playwright_direct' %}
          {% set m_cls = 'm-direct' %}{% set m_lbl = '⚡ Playwright direct' %}
        {% else %}
          {% set m_cls = 'm-fail' %}{% set m_lbl = '✗ Échec' %}
        {% endif %}

        <tr class="{{ 'ok-row' if is_ok else 'fail-row' }}">
          <td><strong>{{ step.step_num }}</strong></td>

          {# Gherkin step #}
          <td>
            <span class="kw {{ kw_cls }}">{{ step.keyword }}</span>
            <div style="margin-top:4px;font-size:.84rem;color:#1f2937">{{ step.gherkin_text }}</div>
          </td>

          {# NLP result #}
          <td>
            <span class="intent">{{ step.intention }}</span>
            <div style="margin-top:5px;display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap">
              {% for ent in step.entites %}
              <span class="entity"><span class="ekey">{{ ent.nom }}</span><span style="opacity:.4">:</span><span class="eval">{{ ent.valeur }}</span></span>
              {% endfor %}
            </div>
          </td>

          {# Generated code #}
          <td>
            <div class="code-lines">
              {% for codeline in step.generated_code %}
              <span class="code-line">{{ codeline }}</span>
              {% endfor %}
            </div>
          </td>

          {# Method #}
          <td>
            <span class="method {{ m_cls }}">{{ m_lbl }}</span>
            {% if step.retry_count > 0 %}<div style="margin-top:4px;font-size:.74rem;color:var(--muted)">{{ step.retry_count }}× retry</div>{% endif %}
          </td>

          {# Status + error #}
          <td>
            <span class="st {{ 'st-ok' if is_ok else 'st-fail' }}">{{ '✓ OK' if is_ok else '✗ FAILED' }}</span>
            {% if step.erreur %}
            <div class="err-box">
              {% if step.erreur_type %}<div class="err-type">{{ step.erreur_type }}</div>{% endif %}
              {% if step.erreur_explication %}<div class="err-exp">{{ step.erreur_explication }}</div>{% endif %}
            </div>
            {% endif %}
          </td>

          {# Duration #}
          <td>
            {% set max_ms = 15000 %}
            {% set pct = [[step.duree_ms / max_ms * 100, 100]|min, 0]|max|int %}
            <div class="dur-bar">
              <div style="font-size:.8rem;white-space:nowrap">{{ "%.0f"|format(step.duree_ms) }} ms</div>
              <div class="bar"><div class="bar-fill {{ 'ok-bar' if is_ok else 'fail-bar' }}" style="width:{{ pct }}%"></div></div>
            </div>
          </td>
        </tr>
        {% endfor %}
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>

  <!-- ── RECOVERY LEGEND ── -->
  <div style="background:var(--card);border-radius:var(--r);padding:18px 22px;margin-top:20px;box-shadow:var(--sh)">
    <div class="sec-title">Légende des méthodes</div>
    <table style="font-size:.83rem">
      <tr>
        <td style="padding:6px 12px 6px 0"><span class="method m-direct">⚡ Playwright direct</span></td>
        <td style="padding:6px 12px;color:var(--muted)">Le locator Playwright a trouvé l'élément directement — aucune récupération nécessaire.</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="padding:6px 12px 6px 0"><span class="method m-fallback">🔍 YOLO+DOM Fallback</span></td>
        <td style="padding:6px 12px;color:var(--muted)">Le locator a échoué → screenshot → YOLO (détection visuelle) + DOM F12 (getBoundingClientRect) → meilleur élément par similarité de texte → action via coordonnées / JS eval.</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="padding:6px 12px 6px 0"><span class="method m-fallback-fail">⚠ Fallback tenté</span></td>
        <td style="padding:6px 12px;color:var(--muted)">Fallback YOLO+DOM tenté mais n'a pas pu récupérer (aucun élément correspondant trouvé sur la page).</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="padding:6px 12px 6px 0"><span class="method m-retry">🔄 Retry + Adaptation</span></td>
        <td style="padding:6px 12px;color:var(--muted)">Échec → AdaptationService diagnostique (popup ? modal ? lenteur ?) → action corrective → nouvel essai.</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="padding:6px 12px 6px 0"><span class="method m-fail">✗ Échec</span></td>
        <td style="padding:6px 12px;color:var(--muted)">Toutes les stratégies ont échoué. Le step est FAILED.</td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </div>

  <div class="footer">Trace générée par <strong>IA Test Agent</strong> · {{ date_generated }}</div>
</div>

<script>
mermaid.initialize({startOnLoad:true,theme:'base',themeVariables:{fontSize:'13px'},flowchart:{useMaxWidth:true,htmlLabels:true}});
</script>
</body>
</html>
